{"tid":1918242,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"早排發咗個夢","createTime":"2020-03-10T03:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T08:34:17.000Z","uid":150100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9a365545d300765e38646f22ae5020645e0388d6","tid":1918242,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T03:23:55.000Z","msg":"冇記錯個夢係唔知做喺街，然後有隻痴線狗乸衝過嚟要搜我身，然後我一拎轉身就攞嘢電鳩我，我越嗌救命佢就電得越勁，佢隔離另一個女警，好似靚女嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拉住佢都唔肯停，起勢咁電鳩me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後突然有個手足唔知係飛出嚟一腳踢開個狗乸，然後我本能意識一招廬山昇龍霸打落隻狗乸度，點知一招就打死咗隻狗乸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後我就乖乖地俾個靚女女警拉，完<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個夢大概係咁，啲細節位唔係好記得，淨係知個夢好逼真，俾人電嗰陣真係好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26484c5af067d02c2e4d7bfb39cc691d43cb1c98","tid":1918242,"uid":145927,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T03:27:32.000Z","msg":"對ching精神狀況表示關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd7b58a84bf4d8a15e0058e663cae7cc22e5c6f","tid":1918242,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26484c5af067d02c2e4d7bfb39cc691d43cb1c98","tid":1918242,"uid":145927,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T03:27:32.000Z","msg":"對ching精神狀況表示關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T03:28:42.000Z","msg":"冇，已經痴咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e802f50ac10f90f1983b62c2cf0a6398857adf2","tid":1918242,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T03:31:23.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"71c44a493cb9997d6d40ead6bd0d4cdda230febd","tid":1918242,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T03:35:11.000Z","msg":"留意